title: Kings Can Fly v1.3.4
description:
Kings Can Fly will soon have your brain sweating as you try to fly the King through his maze-like kingdom. You need a good eye and sharp wits to navigate the towering mountains, spiked gates and dangerous whirlwinds you encounter on the way.

Features:
60+ challenging puzzles
Cute and colorful 3D graphics
Adorable airships
Dangerous spikes
Whirlwinds
Original soundtrack
Easy to use hint system
XPERIA PLAY Optimized

This game requests permissions for the following usage:
Keeping your phone from sleeping to prevent the screen going blank while playing.
Internet access for analytics and improved error reporting (we don't collect private data).
Reading phone state to pause the game when you're being called.

What's new:

Performance improvements
Removed analyics
Fixed a level exploit
Improved device compatibility
